The paper also uses Deep Learning architectures, which falls under Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Bert-based models also suggests a focus on Natural Language Processing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper introduces a new dataset for the Italian language, which could fall under Software Development (cs.SD) as it involves creating a new resource for language processing.
